<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>beer store/orderbeer</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="navtop">
      <ul class="nav">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">HOME</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#">Link</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="#">Link</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img src="beer1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." max-width: 100%; max-height: 400px>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="beer2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." max-width: 100%; max-height: 400px>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="beer3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="..." max-width: 100%; max-height: 400px>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span> 
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div id="beertop">
          <h1>BEER THAILAND</h1>
          <p style="font-size: 25px;"><%-a.length%> product</p>
        </div>
        <div id="covercard">
          <div class="row" >
            <% for(let i =0;i<a.length-2 ;i++) {%> 
              <div class="card" id="cardbeer" >
                  <img src="<%- a[i].img %>.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-title" id="namebeer"><%- a[i].name %></p>
                    <p id="textinfocard"><%- a[i].styleofbeer %> <%- a[i].percentalcohol %> <%- a[i].volume %></p>
                    <p id="pricebeer"><%- a[i].price %> ฿</p>
                    <input type="number" id="inputquantitybeer"style="width: 50px; height: 36px;" value=1><a href="#" class="btn btn-dark" ><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart" id="iconcart"aria-hidden="true"></i>Add to cart</a>
                  </div> 
              </div>
            <%}%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="topicbeerarticles">
          <h2>BEER ARTICLES</h2>
        </div>
        <div class = "row" >
          <div class="card" style="width: 25rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; margin-right: 2rem;">
            <a href="https://thematter.co/social/thai-craft-beer-but-dont-make-in-thai/125582">
              <img src="beerinfo1.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">‘เบียร์ไทยที่ไม่ได้ผลิตในไทย’ สำรวจเบียร์ไทยไปผลิตที่ไหนเมื่อกฎหมายแอลกอฮอล์มีปัญหา</p>
                <h5>Read more</h5>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="width: 25rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; margin-right: 2rem;">
            <a href="https://www.wongnai.com/food-tips/things-you-should-know-about-beer">
              <img src="beerinfo2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">คอเบียร์ต้องรู้! เบียร์มีแบบไหนและดื่มยังไงให้อร่อย?</p>
                <h5>Read more</h5>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="width: 25rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; margin-right: 2rem;">
            <a href="https://urbancreature.co/craft-beer/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=craft-beer">
              <img src="beerinfo3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">คราฟท์เบียร์ไทย ทำไมต้องจดต่างแดน ?</p>
                <h5>Read more</h5>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>   
    </div>
    <div class="navbottom">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-6">
            <p>It is a warning that alcohol is a cause of quarrels and crime.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-3">
            <h4>CONTACT</h4>
            <p>THAWATCHAI JAMNOTHAI</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-3">
            <h4>FOLLOW</h4>
            <div id="iconfollow">
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/thawatchai.jamnothai/"><i class="fa fa-facebook fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
              <a href="https://twitter.com/"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/"><i class="fa fa-youtube-play fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/"><i class="fa fa-instagram fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha256-u7e5khyithlIdTpu22PHhENmPcRdFiHRjhAuHcs05RI=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-JEW9xMcG8R+pH31jmWH6WWP0WintQrMb4s7ZOdauHnUtxwoG2vI5DkLtS3qm9Ekf" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>   
  </body>
</html>
<style>
